
Thowable(parent of all exception)
     Exception(which user can handle to maintain normal execution of a program)
              -checked Exception:(compile time exception or identified by compiler)
                             2 types
                                  - IOException
                                  - SQLException
              -unchecked Exception:(not detected by the compiler/during runtime)
              					  -Runtime Exception
              					          Arthmatic Exception
              					          ArrayOutOfException
              					          etc etc
                                                			
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     Error: which we cannot do anything
     (Example: jvm is not working/cpu is not working)